的<rss version="2.0" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/"><channel><title>医学新闻</title><description>来自 News-Medical.Net - 来自世界各地的最新医学新闻和研究</description><link/>https://www.news-medical.net/<language>英文</language><item><title>SARS-CoV-2 劫持身体的新陈代谢以放大 COVID-19 的严重性</title><description>在 Signal Transduction and Targeted Therapy 杂志上发表的一篇评论文章中，科学家们讨论了由严重急性呼吸系统综合症冠状病毒 2 (SARS-CoV-2) 引发的宿主代谢改变及其对疾病严重程度的影响。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230609/SARS-CoV-2-hijacks-bodys-metabolism-to-amplify-COVID-19-severity.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230609/SARS-CoV-2-hijacks-bodys-metabolism-to-amplify-COVID-19-severity.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=f1675794-6175-4144-a758-59a737336869</guid><pubDate> Fri, 09 Jun 2023 01:04:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="1178" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/images/news/ImageForNews_750568_16862869600292881.jpg" width="2000"><media:description><![CDATA[SARS-CoV-2 hijacks body's metabolism to amplify COVID-19 severity]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>研究揭示了对临床医生同行比较与工作满意度之间关系的见解</title><description>向人们展示他们的行为与同龄人相比如何是改善行为的常用方法。但在全球大流行加剧了医疗保健提供者的工作不满和倦怠之后，关于同行比较对临床医生福祉的潜在负面影响的问题仍然存在。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230609/Study-reveals-insights-into-the-relationship-between-peer-comparison-and-job-satisfaction-among-clinicians.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230609/Study-reveals-insights-into-the-relationship-between-peer-comparison-and-job-satisfaction-among-clinicians.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=7530a5b9-002b-4716-9ec3-0b513c4262f0</guid><pubDate> Fri, 09 Jun 2023 00:31:16 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/7/Pandemic-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Study reveals insights into the relationship between peer comparison and job satisfaction among clinicians]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>全球试验可以通过改变未来的癌症治疗程序来挽救生命</title><description>埃迪斯科文大学 (ECU) 的研究人员正在领导突破性的全球试验，这些试验可以通过在不久的将来改变我们治疗癌症的方式来挽救生命。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230609/Global-trials-could-save-lives-by-changing-treatment-procedure-for-cancer-in-the-future.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230609/Global-trials-could-save-lives-by-changing-treatment-procedure-for-cancer-in-the-future.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=ea036c56-c05f-4a5b-94ab-ab77f0aba122</guid><pubDate> Fri, 09 Jun 2023 00:18:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/7/174318220-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Global trials could save lives by changing treatment procedure for cancer in the future]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>探索血管性痴呆新疗法的可行性</title><description>得益于美国国立卫生研究院 (NIH) 国家神经疾病和中风研究所 (NINDS) 提供的 220 万美元赠款，德克萨斯大学埃尔帕索药学院的研究人员将探索血管性痴呆新疗法的可行性。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230609/Exploring-the-viability-of-a-new-treatment-for-vascular-dementia.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230609/Exploring-the-viability-of-a-new-treatment-for-vascular-dementia.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=2df37325-10e2-4a2a-ab24-25ef0eda8049</guid><pubDate> Fri, 09 Jun 2023 00:10:35 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/7/Dementia-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Exploring the viability of a new treatment for vascular dementia]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>研究携带蚊子的病原体如何影响和感染人体细胞和组织的新平台</title><description>UCF 的一个研究小组用蚊子喜欢叮咬和以其为食的人体细胞设计了组织——；目标是帮助对抗由叮咬昆虫传播的致命疾病。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230609/New-platform-to-study-how-pathogens-carrying-mosquitoes-impact-and-infect-human-cells-and-tissues.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230609/New-platform-to-study-how-pathogens-carrying-mosquitoes-impact-and-infect-human-cells-and-tissues.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=ca03bff4-d694-4333-9f4f-cb58f7651065</guid><pubDate> Fri, 09 Jun 2023 00:06:27 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2016/2/Dengue%2c_zica_and_chikungunya_fever_mosquito_(aedes_aegypti)_on_human_skin-Tacio_Philip_23765b00daa34a4196aa9cea976adde8-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[New platform to study how pathogens carrying mosquitoes impact and infect human cells and tissues]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>研究为欺诈性 Medicare 家庭医疗保健账单的快速传播提供了新见解</title><description>达特茅斯 Geisel 医学院的一组研究人员进行的一项创新研究的结果发表在《社会科学与医学》杂志上，为了解欺诈性 Medicare 家庭医疗保健账单如何在整个美国迅速传播（或扩散）提供了新的见解美国近年来。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230608/Study-offers-new-insights-into-the-rapid-spread-of-fraudulent-Medicare-home-healthcare-billing.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230608/Study-offers-new-insights-into-the-rapid-spread-of-fraudulent-Medicare-home-healthcare-billing.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=43d78978-ecc7-4331-9117-5cc257e32ccd</guid><pubDate> Thu, 08 Jun 2023 23:56:03 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2018/10/shutterstock_532679098_573152c4350d4fe79b49ad0eacf10282-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Study offers new insights into the rapid spread of fraudulent Medicare home healthcare billing]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>消费者认为植物性肉类更健康，但他们准备好用面筋代替牛排了吗？</title><description>研究探索了人们对肉类替代品作为更健康选择的看法，揭示了消费者经常错误判断其营养价值，尤其是蛋白质含量。这强调了对清晰和诚实的营养信息的需求。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230608/Consumers-view-plant-based-meats-as-healthier-but-are-they-ready-to-swap-steaks-for-seitan.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230608/Consumers-view-plant-based-meats-as-healthier-but-are-they-ready-to-swap-steaks-for-seitan.aspx#评论</comments><guid>https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=d87dd673-2c09-4789-9b88-30878e756634</guid><pubDate> Thu, 08 Jun 2023 22:18:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="1333" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/images/news/ImageForNews_750547_16862548923945335.jpg" width="2000"><media:description><![CDATA[Consumers view plant-based meats as healthier, but are they ready to swap steaks for seitan?]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>儿童 MIS-C：揭示了对 COVID-19 的独特自身免疫反应</title><description>该研究表明，MIS-C 患者在感染 SARS-CoV-2 后，会对病毒的 N 蛋白产生独特的免疫反应，表明与自身蛋白 SNX8 存在交叉反应，这可能将感染与随后的炎症联系起来综合征。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230608/MIS-C-in-children-A-distinct-autoimmune-response-to-COVID-19-unveiled.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230608/MIS-C-in-children-A-distinct-autoimmune-response-to-COVID-19-unveiled.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=d4167773-740f-46f2-ae42-1644132553c7</guid><pubDate> Thu, 08 Jun 2023 22:10:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="1499" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/images/news/ImageForNews_750545_16862536544991365.jpg" width="2000"><media:description><![CDATA[MIS-C in children: A distinct autoimmune response to COVID-19 unveiled]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>促进肠道健康：功能性食品和草药在应对 SARS-CoV-2 变体方面显示出希望</title><description>功能性食品和天然草药具有增强免疫功能和维持肠道菌群多样性的潜力。这篇综述探讨了它们在减轻 SARS-CoV-2 变异对肠道健康和整体健康的影响方面的作用。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230608/Gut-health-boost-Functional-foods-and-herbs-show-promise-in-tackling-SARS-CoV-2-variants.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230608/Gut-health-boost-Functional-foods-and-herbs-show-promise-in-tackling-SARS-CoV-2-variants.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=229976fd-6727-4ae0-8093-df3ff72d99f3</guid><pubDate> Thu, 08 Jun 2023 22:01:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="1249" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/images/news/ImageForNews_750541_16862522104994246.jpg" width="2000"><media:description><![CDATA[Gut health boost: Functional foods and herbs show promise in tackling SARS-CoV-2 variants]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>科学家通过合成纳米体平台释放抗病毒能力</title><description>纳米抗体的发现和验证是一类很有前途的生物制剂，可用于病毒感染的预防和治疗，包括通过协同配对增强中和特性的抗 SARS-CoV-2 纳米抗体。该研究证明了纳米抗体在开发针对病毒感染的有效疗法方面的潜力。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230608/Scientists-unlock-virus-fighting-power-with-synthetic-nanobody-platform.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230608/Scientists-unlock-virus-fighting-power-with-synthetic-nanobody-platform.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=0450241c-7687-4b40-b7a9-54475d1c0daa</guid><pubDate> Thu, 08 Jun 2023 21:51:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="1414" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/images/news/ImageForNews_750467_16862234478488217.jpg" width="2000"><media:description><![CDATA[Scientists unlock virus-fighting power with synthetic nanobody platform]]></media:description></media:content></item></channel></rss>